snippet.title: Small Cell - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as a newly born Small Cell trying to understand the purpose of its existence in this puzzle platformer. Guide this mini-hero through an environment populated by many other cells and many secrets.

Demo Available Now on PC. Check out on Steam or itch.io.

#indie #gaming
